# First Times — Hero Robb, ~2012 (ASL 520). Psychological horror.
# No published walkthrough exists — derived from game source (game.aslx).
# The game NEVER calls finish: the four endings park in the "end" room
# ((redemption|ignorance) x (resentment|acceptance) at the Depth mirror).
# This script reaches the BEST ending, Apocatastasis (redemption+acceptance);
# state=Running there is the genuine complete ending.
# The game is driven by AUTHORED one-shot real-time timers (title crawl,
# darkness "heart" chase, booth "neglect" seance, faceless-family chase,
# choice fade) — the harness's tick:N step advances the clock by exactly the
# authored intervals, deterministically (this game is why tick: exists).
# Chain: scalpel + sheet reveal the pregnant doll; cutting the tumor frees
# the web cluster hiding the alabaster egg -> drawer 666's egg hole opens the
# morgue; janitor's riddle ("iron") + can opener; play money (child's chest)
# -> vending machine can -> earrings; needle bear cut open -> needles + safe
# bear; kiss key (fallen snake idol) unlocks the heart room where flowers +
# earrings + bear on the altar open the doll's chest -> taking the red heart
# triggers the darkness chase (69s) which leaves you holding the heart of
# hate; hate into the child doll wrecks the playroom, opening the bedroom
# (notebook -> ticket) and the faceless-family chase where cutting the boy's
# rope with the scalpel = REDEMPTION (and the toy tower); tower unlocks the
# mural stair (plastic tube); ticket in the booth slot summons the dancer's
# suicide seance (90s) leaving the hands of neglect; hands into the teen doll
# unlock the ritual room (syringe plunger); plunger+tube+needle = makeshift
# syringe, filled with the idol's venom; injecting yourself = the choice —
# northwest = ACCEPTANCE; the eyes of suicide appear in the snake's mouth and
# give the mature doll its eyes, yielding the stone knife that cuts the
# fleshy Descent door; the memory windows lead down to the Depth mirror.
